query: SELECT se.id, se.studentId, se.subjectId, se.professorId, se.status, s.name as student_name, sub.name as subject_name FROM student_enrollments se LEFT JOIN students s ON se.studentId = s.id LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON se.subjectId = sub.id LIMIT 10;
